data.description: North Creek's newest ranch/reverse floor plan by Double O Construction. Spacious and open main living area is great for entertaining or keeping connected with the family. Generous room sizes with main level primary suite featuring two closets, double vanity and tiled shower with bench seat. Additional bedroom on main level along with laundry and full bath. Lower level features a large family room plus two additional bedrooms and full bath. Enjoy evenings hanging out on the front porch or back deck. Plenty of unfinished space in the basement for fantastic storage.
